==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Schizopelmous
<hw>Schiz`o*pel"mous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Schizo-</ets> + Gr. <grk>pe`lma</grk> the sole of the
foot.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having the two flexor tendons of
the toes entirely separate, and the <xex>flexor hallucis</xex> going to
the first toe only.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Schizophyte</ent>⟦br⟧
